snippet.textDisplay: Another example of a masterpeice by CokeStudio Pak. The very fact that they fuse traditional styles together and then fuse this fusion with western styles make us love their songs. You are familiar with what you will hear, but still there will always be a surprise. The masti in these songs was kept intact, although a little faster tempo could have made this song more energetic, the rendition stands out unique. The credit for this goes to the director. QB's voice suits her part the best, Farhan's voice does its part. Well done on this one! ❤
